<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5027501>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 & 22. Astiotrema cyclemysi Siddiqi, 1965. 21. A. cyclemysi, ventral view, redrawn from Siddiqi (1965, fig. 1). 22. A. cyclemysi (Syn. Astiotrema lissemydis Agrawal, 1966), ventral view, redrawn from Agrawal (1966a, fig. 11). Abbreviations: AT, anterior testis; Ce, cecum; CP, cirrus-pouch; EP, excretory pore; EV, excretory vesicle; GP, genital pore; OD, ovarian duct; OS, oral sucker; Ov, ovary; Ph, pharynx; PP, pars prostatica; PT, posterior testis; SR, seminal receptacle; SV, seminal vesicle; Ut, uterus; VD, vitelline duct; VF, vitelline follicle; VS, ventral sucker. Scale bars: Fig. 21 = 500 µm; Fig. 22 = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5027501/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

